(56719, x, x, 'So long as violence lurks in your hearts... I... will... return...', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 28347, 0, 'Sha of Violence to Player'),
(56754, x, x, 'The Azure Serpent stirs in the distance!', 41, 0, 100, 0, 0, 28318, 0, 'Azure Serpent to 0'),
(56754, x, x, 'The Azure Serpent moves in to attack!', 41, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Azure Serpent to Gu Cloudstrike'),
(56754, x, x, '%s casts |cFFFF0000|Hspell:107140|h[Magnetic Shroud]|h|r.  Group up to release the healing energy!', 41, 0, 100, 0, 0, 28320, 0, 'Azure Serpent to 0'),
(56754, x, x, '%s casts |cFFFF0000|Hspell:107140|h[Magnetic Shroud]|h|r.  Group up to release the healing energy!', 41, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Azure Serpent to 0'),
(56473, x, x, '|TInterface\\Icons\\inv_sword_24.blp:20|tFlying Snow uses her |cFFFF0000|Hspell:106706|h[Whirling Steel]|h|r technique!', 41, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Flying Snow to 0'),
(56747, x, x, 'Weaklings... let me make room for our guests.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 28322, 0, 'Gu Cloudstrike to Player'),
(56747, x, x, 'Approach... your death awaits.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 28323, 0, 'Gu Cloudstrike to Player'),
(56747, x, x, 'Let me show you my power.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 28323, 0, 'Gu Cloudstrike to 0'),
(56747, x, x, 'Come to me, serpent!  Together we will destroy these intruders.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 28318, 0, 'Gu Cloudstrike to 0'),
(56747, x, x, 'Serpent, charge me with your power!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 28324, 0, 'Gu Cloudstrike to 0'),
(56747, x, x, 'Their energy is strong!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 28320, 0, 'Gu Cloudstrike to Azure Serpent'),
(56747, x, x, 'No, no! Do not fail me!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 28321, 0, 'Gu Cloudstrike to Azure Serpent'),
(56747, x, x, '%s draws power to him...', 41, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Gu Cloudstrike to Azure Serpent'),
(56747, x, x, 'Power! Glorious power!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Gu Cloudstrike to 0'),
(56747, x, x, 'Even together... we failed...', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 28319, 0, 'Gu Cloudstrike to Player'),
(59751, x, x, 'Brothers! Dispose of these insolent outsiders!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 27746, 0, 'Shado-Pan Warden to 0'),
(59751, x, x, 'The Shado-Pan need no outside aid! Remove these interlopers!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 27745, 0, 'Shado-Pan Warden to 0'),
(65407, x, x, 'Welcome, outsiders. Master Snowdrift is waiting for you inside the school. Please remember to show proper respect to the Master.', 12, 0, 100, 2, 0, 0, 0, 'Shado-Pan Novice to Player'),
(56884, x, x, 'Taran Zhu and the Shado-Pan are MINE. Come forward and die by my hand, as all who oppose me shall in the days to come!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 28334, 0, 'Corrupted Taran Zhu to Player'),
(56884, x, x, 'Hatred will consume and conquer all!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 28332, 0, 'Corrupted Taran Zhu to Player'),
(56884, x, x, 'Feed me your hatred!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 28336, 0, 'Corrupted Taran Zhu to Player'),
(56884, x, x, 'No... NO!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 28333, 0, 'Taran Zhu to 0'),
(56884, x, x, 'The Sha of Hatred has fled my body... and the monastery, as well. I must thank you, strangers. The Shado-Pan are in your debt. Now, there is much work to be done...', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 28423, 0, 'Taran Zhu to 0'),
(59811, x, x, 'Shado-Pan Stormbringers react to your presence and begin to |cFFFF0000|Hspell:115009|h[Focus Energy]|h|r!', 41, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Unstable Energy to Shado-Pan Stormbringer'),
(56541, x, x, 'Very well then, outsiders. Let us see your true strength.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 27628, 0, 'Master Snowdrift to 0'),
(56541, x, x, '|TInterface\\Icons\\inv_weapon_hand_30.blp:20|tMaster Snowdrift uses his |cFFFF0000|Hspell:106853|h[Fists of Fury]|h|r technique!', 41, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Master Snowdrift to 0'),
(56541, x, x, '|TInterface\\Icons\\spell_nature_earthbind.blp:20|tMaster Snowdrift uses his |cFFFF0000|Hspell:106434|h[Tornado Kick]|h|r!', 41, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Master Snowdrift to 0'),
(56541, x, x, 'Skill with a weapon is but a physical manifestation of one''s martial strength. Let me show you what spiritual power is!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 27629, 0, 'Master Snowdrift to 0'),
(56541, x, x, 'Master Snowdrift vanishes to the shadows and creates duplicate illusions of himself! Strike the illusions to dispel them!', 41, 0, 100, 14, 0, 0, 0, 'Master Snowdrift to 0'),
(56541, x, x, 'When I was but a cub I could scarcely throw a punch, but after years of training I can do so much more!', 14, 0, 100, 23, 0, 27630, 0, 'Master Snowdrift to 0'),
(56541, x, x, 'Master Snowdrift attacks you with his hand to hand techniques!', 41, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Master Snowdrift to 0'),
(56870, x, x, 'You!  You have allowed the Sha to reawaken after all these years!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Master Snowdrift to Player'),
(56870, x, x, 'If you truly wish to undo what your kind have wrought upon our land you must first prove yourselves here in our school.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Master Snowdrift to Player'),
(56870, x, x, 'First, you will face our initiates...', 14, 0, 100, 397, 0, 27632, 0, 'Master Snowdrift to Player'),
(56870, x, x, 'Where one falls, another will rise to take their place.', 14, 0, 100, 397, 0, 0, 0, 'Master Snowdrift to Shado-Pan Novice'),
(56870, x, x, 'You have bested our most junior of students.  Now you will face two of my most senior.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Master Snowdrift to Shado-Pan Novice'),
(56870, x, x, 'Flying Snow!  Fragrant Lotus!  Step forward!', 14, 0, 100, 22, 0, 27636, 0, 'Master Snowdrift to Shado-Pan Novice'),
(56870, x, x, 'You have bested my prize students. Perhaps you can be of use to us after all...', 14, 0, 100, 21, 0, 27633, 0, 'Master Snowdrift to 0'),
(56870, x, x, 'As my master once said, "You cannot truly know someone until you fight them."', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 27634, 0, 'Master Snowdrift to 0'),
(56870, x, x, 'Come forward, so that we may be properly introduced.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 27635, 0, 'Master Snowdrift to 0'),
(56767, x, x, 'Shado-Pan Fire Archers appear on the rooftops!', 41, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Shado-Pan Fire Archer to Player'),
(56767, x, x, 'The Shado-Pan Archers disappear!', 41, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Shado-Pan Fire Archer to Player'),
(64549, x, x, 'Shado-Pan Ice Archers appear on the rooftops!', 41, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Shado-Pan Ice Archer to Player'),
(64549, x, x, 'The Shado-Pan Archers disappear!', 41, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Shado-Pan Ice Archer to Player');
